MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 1269

CREATING AND DESIGNATING CERTAIN PARCELS OF LAND SITUATED AT FORT BONIFACIO GLOBAL CITY, TAGUIG, METRO MANILA, AS “INFORMATION TECHNOLOGY PARK” PURSUANT TO REPUBLIC ACT NO. 7916, AS AMENDED BY REPUBLIC ACT NO. 8748

Pursuant to the powers vested in me under Republic Act No. 7916, otherwise known as the Special Economic Zone Act of 1995 , as amended by Republic Act No. 8748, and upon recommendation of the Board of Directors of the Philippine Economic Zone Authority, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO, President of the Republic of the Philippines, do hereby create and designate as Information Technology Park, subject to the provisions of Republic Act No. 7916 as amended, its Implementing Rules and Regulations, and Resolution No. 00-411 dated 29 December 2000 as amended by Resolution No. 04-295 dated 20 September 2004 and Resolution No. 05-270 dated 12 August 2005 as amended by Resolution No. 06-280 dated 27 June 2006 and further amended by Resolution No. 06-414 dated 12 September 2006 of the Board of Directors of the Philippine Economic Zone Authority (PEZA), certain parcels of land located at Fort Bonifacio Global City, Taguig, Metro Manila, containing an area of ONE HUNDRED FORTY THOUSAND FOUR HUNDRED SIXTY SIX (140,466) SQUARE METERS , more or less, as defined by the following technical descriptions:

